sentences.english: The torch will travel the length of Britain during its 70-day relay.
sentences.chinese: 火炬傳遞將在英國國內進行，持續70天。

sentences.english: So, what was the concept Akon and Jackson tried to deliver on the song?
sentences.chinese: 那麼阿肯和傑克遜試圖通過這首歌傳遞什麼理念呢？

sentences.english: The value passed to the actions should be comma-delimited lists of values.
sentences.chinese: 傳遞給動作的值應該是以逗號分隔的值列表。

sentences.english: During the war, our army often used letters attached with a chicken feather to deliver important messages.
sentences.chinese: 戰爭時期我軍經常用雞毛信傳遞重要信息。

sentences.english: Please note that the activation code can be used only on a single phone and is not transferrable .
sentences.chinese: 請注意激活碼只能在一臺手機上使用，不可以傳遞。

sentences.english: Therefore, HR becomes a kind of pass-through in the information cycle.
sentences.chinese: 因此，人力資源人員在信息循環中承擔傳遞的角色。

sentences.english: They bandied the ball from player to player while they waited the game to start.
sentences.chinese: 他們在等比賽開始的時候把球在隊員之間來回傳遞。

sentences.english: This table can also be made to send non-return of the source of signal transmission path .
sentences.chinese: 此表也有作向發送者返回非傳遞信號的源路徑。

sentences.english: The Transfer Matrix Method (TMM) and the Finite Element Method (FEM) are two ordinary calculating methods for rotary system.
sentences.chinese: 傳遞矩陣法和有限元法是轉子動力學分析的常用方法。

sentences.english: The router's role is then to move traffic between the VLANs.
sentences.chinese: 這時，路由器的作用就是在VLAN之間傳遞流量。

sentences.english: Get your brand message out there and don’t waiver on it.
sentences.chinese: 傳遞你的品牌信息，別放棄。

sentences.english: Invokes a method of a prototype-based object, passing in the specified arguments.
sentences.chinese: 調用基於原型的對象的方法，在指定的參數中傳遞。

sentences.english: A bridge will simply send packets from the wire to the wireless and back.
sentences.chinese: 網橋僅僅在有線網和無線網之間傳遞數據包。

sentences.english: The transfer function of piezoelectric transducers has been deduced in the paper.
sentences.chinese: 推導出壓電式傳感器的傳遞函數。

sentences.english: There eis plenty of time for this emotional hand-off.
sentences.chinese: 人類有充足的時間進行這種情感的傳遞。

sentences.english: Soldiers used smoke in the day time and fire at night to deliver the message.
sentences.chinese: 士兵們在白天用烽煙，夜間用篝火傳遞消息。
